Tak perlu.

187
00:30:13,637 --> 00:30:14,836
Maaf.

188
00:30:19,137 --> 00:30:22,447
Hei, wanita yang kukenal...

189
00:30:23,947 --> 00:30:26,647
...selalu mengatakan mereka minta
maaf...

190
00:30:26,776 --> 00:30:28,747
