...aku akhirnya bisa tahu
bagaimana wajah aslimu.

325
00:44:54,217 --> 00:44:56,546
Baek Joo Ran.

326
00:44:57,387 --> 00:44:59,017
Bagian belakang kepalamu bagus.

327
00:44:59,916 --> 00:45:00,927
Hei...

328
00:45:01,427 --> 00:45:02,927
Itu menonjol.

329
