Ayo kita adakan acara pernikahan.

418
01:00:07,001 --> 01:00:10,371
Ri Won, ayo kita adakan
acara pernikahan, ya?

419
01:00:12,081 --> 01:00:13,541
Terima kasih.

420
01:00:17,311 --> 01:00:19,550
Kenapa kau jadi banyak uban sekarang?

421
01:00:20,150 --> 01:00:23,090
Aigoo. Aku 'kan sudah kakek-kakek sekarang.

422
01:00:25,221 --> 01:00:27,360
Waktu kau pertama kali datang
ke sekolah kita..,

423
01:00:27,360 --> 01:00:28,590
